title: Star Wars: The Clone Wars
fullTitle: Star Wars: The Clone Wars (TV Series 2008–2020)

episodes.title: The Unknown
episodes.plot: Clone trooper Tup is suffering from a severe neurological disorder that causes the death of a Jedi master. Trying to find the motives for the assassination, Anakin escorts Tup back to Kamino for examination.

episodes.title: Conspiracy
episodes.plot: Clone trooper Tup is undergoing a medical examination in the sterile laboratories of Kamino to find the motives for his shocking attack on the Jedi Master. For the examination to succeed, trooper Fives must enter the depth of Tup's mind.

episodes.title: Fugitive
episodes.plot: Tup's body is transported back to Coruscant where it is to be examined by the Chancellor's personal physician, while Fives furtively investigates his death with the help of a droid.

episodes.title: Orders
episodes.plot: Fives believes he's uncovered a major conspiracy regarding the mysterious actions of clone trooper Tup, and finds himself on-the-run after he's falsely accused of attempting to murder the Chancellor.

episodes.title: An Old Friend
episodes.plot: While on Scipio to fund a mercy mission, Senator Amidala is called upon by an old friend to help uncover corruption in the Banking Clan.

episodes.title: The Rise of Clovis
episodes.plot: Clovis and Padmé head back to Coruscant to expose the financial corruption of the Banking Clan.

episodes.title: Crisis at the Heart
episodes.plot: After making a deal with Count Dooku to resuscitate the ailing Banking Clan, Clovis finds himself as a pawn in Dooku's designs.

episodes.title: The Disappeared: Part 1
episodes.plot: The peaceful world of Bardotta and its mystic ways are threatened by an ancient prophecy, and its top spiritual leaders have vanished.

episodes.title: The Disappeared: Part 2
episodes.plot: Jar Jar Binks' beloved Queen Julia of the planet Bardotta has been abducted by the bloodthirsty Frangawl Cult to fulfill a dark and ancient prophecy.

episodes.title: The Lost One
episodes.plot: A Jedi mission finds a lightsaber belonging to the long-dead Master Sifo-Dyas, prompting Yoda, Obi-Wan and Anakin to begin an investigation into his decade-old disappearance.

episodes.title: Voices
episodes.plot: Yoda is deeply unsettled when he hears a voice from beyond the grave - the voice of Qui-Gon Jinn.

episodes.title: Destiny
episodes.plot: Letting the Force guide him, Yoda voyages into the heart of the galaxy to an ancient world that is one of the wellsprings of the Force and the source of midi-chlorians.

episodes.title: Sacrifice
episodes.plot: After many grueling trials, Yoda next travels to the ancient Sith home world of Moraband, where he must face an ancient evil determined to rule the galaxy.
